## Full License

For the complete, official AGPLv3 license text, see:
https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html

## How AGPLv3 Affects SaaS

**Important:** If you offer ExecutionPolicy Foundation as a SaaS or over a network, you MUST make the source code available to all users.

Example: If you run a cloud service using this software, users must be able to request the source code.

## When to Use AGPLv3

✓ Open source projects  
✓ Internal company tools (non-SaaS)  
✓ Educational projects  
✓ Community contributions  

❌ Commercial software (use MIT instead)  
❌ SaaS without code disclosure (use MIT or Professional Support)  
❌ Closed-source projects (use MIT instead)  

